<font size="2" color="#505050">Hello!<br><br>

I am hosting another officer meeting this Friday, April 19th, 2002 at 9PM EDT 8PM CDT 7PM MDT and 6PM PDT.<br><br>

I promised Sunseeker we'd have a meeting that isn't the result of a major issue =)  The meeting will go over more of the Guild Charter and we have 5 officer positions open for promotion due to some players who have left.<br><br>

Attendance is not mandantory.. We will be holding it in a EQ chat channel in the game, so you don't have to go anywhere in particular.  I do request, however, that you not be fighting with battlespam during the meeting as this prohibits our productivity.<br><br>

Thank you as always!<br>
-=Sumadi Silversalt<br><br>

<b>Note: Date changed from Wednesday to Friday because I realized that it conflicted with the Befallen Raid.<br></font>
